{"tid":813440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港根本係由耶教統治","createTime":"2018-09-10T12:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T13:04:31.000Z","uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6206e1277fe0bd3a737b4805de3611019a9cfec9","tid":813440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"細個學校迫啲無神論小孩感謝主耶穌、稱耶穌是主、讀聖經考聖經唔準質疑聖經、慶祝復活節同聖誕節；<br />\n出嚟工作，管理層多數是耶人；<br />\n睇醫生，信耶唔使食藥，不信的要強制留醫；<br />\n法庭入面耶人強姦未成年處女判社會服務令...；<br />\n監獄𥚃信耶有優待，不信耶日日被阿sir打直至你信耶；<br />\n結婚要喺教堂結；<br />\n然後再發現大部分獻世派、多數嘅泛民、佔中發起人、傳媒高層以至港獨首領都係耶人"},{"pid":"b24466222181b2eb3c44ccc3f37dd41f4bd5918e","tid":813440,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"神的國"},{"pid":"56e34cdea4041e19af229f7001ce02cc0afc7afa","tid":813440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b24466222181b2eb3c44ccc3f37dd41f4bd5918e","tid":813440,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"神的國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"香港獨立後咪又係基督徒陳浩天話事"},{"pid":"42f354c26d8f53bcf8421cd3c4ab5af6f4d158b5","tid":813440,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd965567c2d3546f93bf6a4677fe796600583547","tid":813440,"uid":155137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"連特首參選都係神嘅旨意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae78520a41b034b86995af74c0dade2b104d7a4","tid":813440,"uid":2590,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T18:25:20.000Z","msg":"有咩問題，世界上真係有神丫嘛"},{"pid":"d2fb766b38389e92a3a3a6aa60e1a8f27b033c7b","tid":813440,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fae78520a41b034b86995af74c0dade2b104d7a4","tid":813440,"uid":2590,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"ci